### Solicitar registro
POST http://localhost:3000/registration/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "profession": "desenvolvedor",
  "bio": "Backend developer"
}

### Listar solicitações de registro (autenticado)
GET http://localhost:3000/registration/requests?status=PENDING&page=1&perPage=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

### Aprovar solicitação de registro (autenticado)
POST http://localhost:3000/registration/replace-with-uuid/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

### Rejeitar solicitação de registro (autenticado)
POST http://localhost:3000/registration/replace-with-uuid/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

{
  "reason": "Perfil não atende aos requisitos"
}
